---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';

const lastUpdated = 'April 2, 2026';
---

<Layout
  title="Terms of Service"
  description="Terms of Service for CAPP GAMES — covering all games, properties, and services."
>
  <section class="page-header">
    <div class="container">
      <h1>Terms of <span class="gold">Service</span></h1>
      <div class="gold-divider"></div>
      <p class="updated">Last updated: {lastUpdated}</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="tos-section">
    <div class="container tos-content">

      <p class="intro">
        These Terms of Service govern your use of all games, websites, and services operated by
        <strong>CAPP GAMES</strong>, including but not limited to <em>capp-games.com</em> and any
        other CAPP GAMES properties. By accessing or using any of these services, you agree to
        these terms.
      </p>

      <div class="tos-block">
        <h2>1. Intellectual Property</h2>
        <p>
          All original game code, mechanics, design, branding, and creative work published across
          CAPP GAMES properties is owned by CAPP GAMES. This includes game rules, UI design, game
          systems, original artwork, written content, and the CAPP GAMES name and logo.
        </p>
        <p>
          You may not copy, reproduce, redistribute, or reverse-engineer any part of our games or
          services without prior written permission from CAPP GAMES.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="tos-block">
        <h2>2. Acceptable Use</h2>
        <p>When using any CAPP GAMES service, you agree not to:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Cheat, exploit bugs, or use unauthorized tools to gain an unfair advantage</li>
          <li>Attempt to extract, scrape, or reproduce game assets or source code</li>
          <li>Interfere with the normal operation of our games or servers</li>
          <li>Use our services for any unlawful purpose</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="tos-block">
        <h2>3. Free-to-Play Games</h2>
        <p>
          Our browser games are provided free of charge. We reserve the right to modify, update,
          or discontinue any game or feature at any time without prior notice.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="tos-block">
        <h2>4. User Content & Accounts</h2>
        <p>
          If you create an account or submit any content through our services, you grant CAPP GAMES
          the right to store and use that content as necessary to provide the service. We reserve
          the right to remove any user content or suspend any account that violates these terms.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="tos-block">
        <h2>5. No Warranty</h2>
        <p>
          All CAPP GAMES services are provided "as is" without warranty of any kind. We are not
          liable for any downtime, data loss, bugs, or damages arising from your use of our
          services.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="tos-block">
        <h2>6. Changes to These Terms</h2>
        <p>
          We may update these Terms of Service at any time. Continued use of our services after
          changes are posted constitutes acceptance of the new terms. The "last updated" date at
          the top of this page reflects the most recent revision.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="tos-block">
        <h2>7. Contact</h2>
        <p>
          If you have questions about these Terms of Service, you can reach us through the
          <a href="/about#contact" class="inline-link">contact form</a> on our About page.
        </p>
      </div>

    </div>
  </section>

</Layout>

<style>
  .page-header {
    padding: 4rem 0 2rem;
    background:
      radial-gradient(ellipse 60% 40% at 50% 0%, rgba(245,192,0,0.05) 0%, transparent 70%),
      var(--bg);
  }

  .page-header h1 {
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .updated {
    color: var(--text-dim);
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    margin: 0.5rem 0 0;
  }

  .tos-section {
    padding: 3rem 0 5rem;
  }

  .tos-content {
    max-width: 720px;
  }

  .intro {
    color: var(--text-dim);
    line-height: 1.8;
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
  }

  .tos-block {
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
    padding-bottom: 2.5rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
  }

  .tos-block:last-child {
    border-bottom: none;
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  .tos-block h2 {
    font-size: 1rem;
    color: var(--gold);
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.03em;
  }

  .tos-block p {
    color: var(--text-dim);
    line-height: 1.8;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
  }

  .tos-block p:last-child { margin-bottom: 0; }

  .tos-block ul {
    color: var(--text-dim);
    line-height: 1.8;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    padding-left: 1.5rem;
    margin: 0.5rem 0 0;
  }

  .tos-block ul li {
    margin-bottom: 0.4rem;
  }

  .inline-link {
    color: var(--gold);
    text-decoration: none;
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(245,192,0,0.3);
    transition: border-color 0.2s;
  }
  .inline-link:hover { border-color: var(--gold); }
</style>
